Class ContentChange

java.lang.Object
  edu.bonn.cs.wmp.awarenesswidgets.ContentChange
Direct Known Subclasses:
LineChange, ViewportChange
public abstract class ContentChange
extends Object

Super class for all types of content changes. Content changes are exchanged between WMPViews and their corresponding WMPAwarenessWidgets and sometimes - e.g. in case of the ViewportChange in the form of beans - even between clients.
